    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-12-17T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-12-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="689" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d689">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">
                        <persName type="from">Mavroyeni Bey</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Imperial Legation of Turkey</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-12-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 17,
                                    1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. <hi rend="smallcaps">Secretary of State</hi>: I have the pleasure to
                            give herewith copy of a telegram which I have this instant received from
                            His Excellency Tevfik Pasha, conceived in these terms: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>Mr. Terrell has addressed to me two notes to express his
                                    satisfaction at the conduct observed by our authorities during
                                    the late disorders, and in particular renders homage to the
                                    efforts which they have put forth for the protection of the life
                                    and the property of the missionaries and American citizens at
                                    Harpoot, Marsovan, Aintab, and Marash.</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <p>Be pleased to accept, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Mavroyeni.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
